      "review_summary": "The PR adds a pre-pass to `repairToolUseResultPairing` that skips later assistant messages when all extracted tool-call ids were seen before, plus two transcript repair tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +31, Tests +72. Total +103 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: no. high-confidence live reproduction of the reported lossless-claw legacy database case is available in this checkout. The PR's introduced risk is source-reproducible: the new check only looks at extracted tool-call ids and can drop assistant messages with distinct non-tool content.",
